{"tid":2341943,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"阿富汗捕10名中国間諜 要求北京道歉","createTime":"2020-12-26T18:03:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T18:16:08.000Z","uid":130406,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1c5a9a7f03db9cc9a00c000cc4a97f08e7a0a98b","tid":2341943,"uid":130406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T18:03:52.000Z","msg":"<strong>阿富汗情報當局稱，他們搗毀了一個與恐怖組織有關的中國間諜小組，10名中國公民被捕，其中至少兩人與塔利班分支恐怖組織哈卡尼網絡有聯繫。喀布爾當局要求北京道歉。</strong><br />\n<br />\n法廣RFI駐該地區記者索尼亞&middot;加紮利（Sonia Ghezali）報道，阿富汗情報部門認為中國公民間諜網的首腦之一是Li YangYang (音譯李陽洋)。當局在他位於喀布爾的家中發現了武器、彈藥和爆炸物。其他8中國公民與他一起被阿富汗情報部門逮捕。據說他一直與塔利班武裝分支&ldquo;哈卡尼&rdquo;（Haqqani）恐怖網絡保持聯繫。<br />\n阿富汗情報部門稱，這名中國間諜正在尋求有關 &quot;基地 &quot;組織及新疆維吾爾人在阿富汗東部省份可能存在的信息。近年來，有些激進維吾爾人加入 &quot;基地 &quot;組織的 &quot;東突厥斯坦伊斯蘭運動 &quot; （ETIM）小團體。四年前，該團體宣布向中國發動聖戰，要 &quot;把新疆從共產黨侵略者手中解放出來&quot;。直到最近，據說有一些維吾爾人可能加入了 &quot;伊斯蘭國 &quot;在阿富汗的分支。<br />\n另據FX168財經報社(香港)12月25日報道，在喀布爾瑟普爾經營餐館的女性Sha Hung（音譯沙紅）也被逮捕。阿富汗反恐官員說道：&ldquo;阿富汗國家情報局從她的住處取回爆炸物和相關犯罪的證據。並說，他們（中國公民）都持續與&ldquo;哈卡尼&rdquo;網絡保持聯繫。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n阿富汗總統加尼 (Ashraf Ghani) 政府表示，已要求中國道歉，否則將不會釋放這些中國公民，而且會對他們提起訴訟。喀布爾的高級外交官指出，10名中國公民里至少有2人與&ldquo;哈卡尼&rdquo;網絡保持聯繫，而該網絡被視為兼作塔利班恐怖組織的刀劍。<br />\n<br />\n印度斯坦時報(Hindustan Times)引述喀布爾反恐官員指出，被拘留的李陽洋Li Yangyang自7月以來持續為中國情報部門工作，他於12月10日在喀布爾附近的家中，被阿富汗國家情報局逮捕。<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\"><a href=\"https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20201226-%E9%98%BF%E5%AF%8C%E6%B1%97%E6%8D%9510%E5%90%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%96%93%E8%AB%9C%EF%BC%8C%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89?fbclid=IwAR2sLT6K_MCMWGgfy-PRjAwuYGuV9uNyMPp1HMADU91AiHSoFzWPuaLn6fM&amp;ref=fb_i\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Fcn%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20201226-%25E9%2598%25BF%25E5%25AF%258C%25E6%25B1%2597%25E6%258D%259510%25E5%2590%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2596%2593%25E8%25AB%259C%25EF%25BC%258C%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E9%2581%2593%25E6%25AD%2589%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2sLT6K_MCMWGgfy-PRjAwuYGuV9uNyMPp1HMADU91AiHSoFzWPuaLn6fM%26ref%3Dfb_i&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUkpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=c14e670e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20201226-%E9%98%BF%E5%AF%8C%E6%B1%97%E6%8D%9510%E5%90%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%96%93%E8%AB%9C%EF%BC%8C%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89?fbclid=IwAR2sLT6K_MCMWGgfy-PRjAwuYGuV9uNyMPp1HMADU91AiHSoFzWPuaLn6fM&amp;ref=fb_i</a></span>"},{"pid":"b25be048248ec9ade76d4227e9b7efcd74987911","tid":2341943,"uid":194298,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T18:04:40.000Z","msg":"打鳩佢啦仲道歉"},{"pid":"f8fd89fb853dfd93e081ed8be0a27c3f3989a214","tid":2341943,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T18:05:29.000Z","msg":"中國對自己啲人民都草菅人命㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2d394032c72dafe64050717fc5e56e246bc7846","tid":2341943,"uid":186882,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T18:06:50.000Z","msg":"話中共係犯罪集團真係唔夠<br />\n根本就係恐怖分子既final boss"},{"pid":"94c6e255bbc332195a6377758e92984b3cd99b1b","tid":2341943,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T18:08:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a8c67e462116a21c6dce2e8f55f934bf0dc244f","tid":2341943,"uid":130406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T18:08:57.000Z","msg":"道歉？支那理得個十條韭菜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分鐘支共有份養起啲塔利班"},{"pid":"bbe50b8612880307bad63f416e13a0724441ab5a","tid":2341943,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T18:09:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"946be645474360f24df879b511362444e767013b","tid":2341943,"uid":36178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T18:10:44.000Z","msg":"一早講過支那同塔利班有關係"},{"pid":"4f25118f80b49792f361343fc727d10b2dfd3cf2","tid":2341943,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T18:12:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>10名中國公民被捕，<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">其中至少兩人與塔利班分支恐怖組織哈卡尼網絡有聯繫</span></span></strong>。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好仆街！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1254a2cd3d007d6ab2ca209bf2bc591fa6571df3","tid":2341943,"uid":171313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T18:13:38.000Z","msg":"拖班蝗蟲出黎鞭屍"},{"pid":"aac32f965132b8b109252ea1170744d69afbdf11","tid":2341943,"uid":258903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T18:15:03.000Z","msg":"大陸有無十個阿富汗人可以捉番做人質<br />\n代入中共就自然識諗"},{"pid":"e0187ec4c953252d3514c06dee8b89026be2ee33","tid":2341943,"uid":370061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T18:16:08.000Z","msg":"道歉？<br />\n支共：塔利班，我呢到有批好平嘅軍火......"}]}